Global Dry Granulator Equipment Market Insights
Dry Granulator Equipment Market size was valued at USD 1.5 Billion in 2022 and is projected to reach USD 2.8 Billion by 2030, growing at a CAGR of 8.5% from 2024 to 2030.

Dry Granulator Equipment Market Overview
The dry granulator equipment market is valued at approximately USD 1.5 billion in 2025 and is expected to grow at a CAGR of 5.4% over the forecast period. The market is driven by the increasing demand for efficient and high-speed granulation processes across various industries such as pharmaceuticals, chemicals, and food processing. The adoption of dry granulation technologies offers several advantages, such as reduced production costs, minimal equipment maintenance, and enhanced product quality. Furthermore, the rising focus on minimizing the use of solvents and improving sustainability in manufacturing processes further supports the growth of the dry granulator equipment market. Strict regulatory requirements in the pharmaceutical sector are also fueling the demand for advanced granulation equipment, further propelling market growth.

